<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #d4af37;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-top: none;
            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .quote-box {
            padding: 25px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
        }

        .quote {
            margin: 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #444;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .action-box {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 35px;
        }

        .btn {
            background: #d4af37;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #999;
        }

        hr {
            border: 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Rerendet Coffee</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">We're Sad to See You Go, {{firstName}}</div>
            <p class="message">Your Rerendet Coffee account has been successfully deleted as per your request.</p>
            <p class="message">We're truly sorry to see you leave our coffee community. It was a pleasure serving you,
                and we value the time you spent with us.</p>

            <div class="quote-box">
                <p class="quote">"A good cup of coffee is always waiting for you should you decide to return."</p>
            </div>

            <p class="message">If there was anything we could have done better, or if you'd like to share your reason
                for leaving, we'd love to hear your feedback.</p>

            <div class="action-box">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}" class="btn">Visit Our Shop</a>
            </div>

            <hr>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-align: center;">This is an automated message to confirm your
                account deletion. Your data has been removed from our active systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2025 Rerendet Coffee. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>